{"tid":1342961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再講有手足係元朗比人打啦！","createTime":"2019-07-21T18:10:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T00:15:33.000Z","uid":39205,"like":108,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2e3a969de8134f374fa028743a2f529695fe14ef","tid":1342961,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:10:12.000Z","msg":"係有<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">普通市民</span></span></strong>比人打呀，個班白衫黑社會係見人就打，大肚婆小朋友呀伯都打架我屌你老母。<br />\n<br />\n唔好再話有示威者、黑衫、手足比人打，係普通市民呀，<span style=\"color: orange;\">唔好比任何機會黑警或者政府將兩件事拉埋一齊講</span>，一陣講撚到因為示威先有呢件事咁。<br />\n<br />\n兩單野黎架，示威還示威一單，<span style=\"color: orange;\">宜家另一單係有普通市民比黑社會追打而警方無作出任何行動甚至放任佢地呀屌你老母！</span><br />\n<br />\n上次沙田你都仲可以賴係示威者入商場先會影響到普通市民，今次人地放工食完飯一家大細搭地鐵返屋企都比人打呀，煲撚大佢我睇你點拆屌你老母！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">同埋上環仲清緊場架，大家唔好忘記左佢地呀！</span></span>"},{"pid":"b7e41760ea934c99841474190bbe7d1144e104f4","tid":1342961,"uid":69810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:10:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c768adbb1666e044bc65a437501ce171ab2e1be2","tid":1342961,"uid":39205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:12:24.000Z","msg":"屌你老母玩撚大左啦死黑警，我睇你點撚樣收科！"},{"pid":"ad5250533803e4a00a614a3b360097b3133b47a4","tid":1342961,"uid":179649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:12:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b535535648831087bbb8420fc194e4e4754625","tid":1342961,"uid":17623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:14:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"54fba4d9b17aa3e967c76f51194431e5641ca2a8","tid":1342961,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:14:36.000Z","msg":"推呀屌！比啲中立撚再睇下，你再唔企出黎搭車返屋企都比人打死呀！"},{"pid":"6567ed29bc5f2e0db15b47c477cb8c6cea0110c0","tid":1342961,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0